      "beat_id": "B07",
      "t_start": 60.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10.0,
      "narration_text": "The imaginary part is the only place where direction of motion lives. The phase \u2014 the winding rate of the helix \u2014 is the momentum. Without the imaginary part, momentum is ambiguous.",
